{
  "stem": "6195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Cracow, only one building got hit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There is, there is a reason behind it, too, because Cracow is over 1,000 years old, and [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Hitler ?] obviously wanted to preserve it because, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, of the antiques and-- Well, then suddenly, we heard on the 3rd of September, a German voice, language saying that they have reclaimed the German city of Cracow.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Cracow was never German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, Austro-Hungarian, but generally, it-- it was a genuine Polish territory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they warned not to leave homes and not to come to the windows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all kept together, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my sister and I and my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we heard the boots, the marching soldiers going through, we just went.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And through the curtain, we looked, and we couldn't believe our eyes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "11 people were already hanging.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They hung 11 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mixed, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jews and non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It stretched from the corner, opposite our building, to the corner, to the next corner of the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was, that was something we thought that we see in a dream.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It can't be real, but it was real.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It was real, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, then the tragedy started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Next, they were allowed to queue up at the bakery for bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The queues were so long, and the Germans are-- were grabbing from the queue, taking people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody knew where they were, never coming back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was terribly, terribly frightening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the same time, they passed [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a law, I suppose-- it was hanging on the walls everywhere-- that the doors of our flats should be forever open, day and night.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
